{
  "stem": "3952.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I'm quite tired already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think this will be the finishing-- the finishing part of it, because there's just so much I can take of this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm born-- I was born on the 5th of May.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The 5th of May, for me, is a very, very special-- special date, because a few things happened on the 5th of May.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was liberated on the 5th of May, 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the significance of the liberation was that, before that, I had a dream I spoke to my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I have to give you a little bit of something that happened on the 2nd of May.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the 2nd of May, somebody let out a rumor that the Americans are here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all of us in our block started jumping down from our cots and jump in the middle of block.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Americans are here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We  are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After about 10, 15 minutes of such-- such happiness, the kapos came in and started beating us up, and out to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't know-- for some reason we were late to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's probably why somebody made that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The disappointment-- to describe to you the disappointment [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of what happened then, I cannot-- I am not capable of describing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't have words to describe to you what kind of disappointment that was, that the-- that after we thought we are free, that we have to go back to work and everything like normal.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have a friend-- I had a friend who killed himself that day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That night, when we came back, he covered himself with a blanket and he said he doesn't want to live.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He strangled himself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] from Sieghart.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I knew him very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
